01:30:16,577 --> 01:30:19,621
Better to listen than to talk.

1037
01:30:21,040 --> 01:30:22,666
I believe you.

1038
01:30:22,834 --> 01:30:26,128
Don't search
for all the answers at once.

1039
01:30:27,004 --> 01:30:32,342
A path is formed
by laying one stone at a time.

1040
01:30:36,097 --> 01:30:40,767
One person saw the third man.

1041
01:30:40,935 --> 01:30:45,063
Three have seen him, yes,

1042
01:30:45,231 --> 01:30:47,149
but not his body.

1043
01:30:47,316 --> 01:30:51,486
One only known to you.

1044
01:30:51,654 --> 01:30:53,738
Ready now to talk.

1045
01:30:56,909 --> 01:30:59,536
One more thing.

1046
01:30:59,704 --> 01:31:02,372
You forgot something.

1047
01:31:04,375 --> 01:31:05,959
What?

1048
01:32:11,442 --> 01:32:13,526
Laura! Laura!

1049
01:32:28,960 --> 01:32:31,503
Laura!

